plot: Michael is put in an awkward position when Jan sues Dunder Mifflin for wrongful termination and he is deposed as a witness. Kelly begins smack-talking Pam after Darryl beats Jim at ping-pong.

Michael and Jan go to New York since Jan sued Dunder Mifflin over her termination, thinking it was her breast implants that caused it. Things go awry when different scenarios arise, such as the photo Michael took of Jan on their Christmas break, showing they had a relationship earlier then announced. Back at Scranton, over Jim's numerous losses against Darryl in ping-pong, Kelly has been smack- talking Pam. To get rid of this problem, Pam wants Jim to practice and have a rematch against Darryl.—James Hake
